==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Stereotyped
<hw>Ste"re*o*typed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Formed into, or printed from, stereotype plates.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Fig.: Formed in a fixed, unchangeable manner;
<as>as, <ex>stereotyped</ex> opinions</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Our civilization, with its <qex>stereotyped</qex> ways and smooth
conventionalities.</q> <rj><qau>J. C. Shairp.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stereotyper</ent>⟦br⟧
